text: San José is the first canton of San José Province in Costa Rica. The capital of Costa Rica, San José, is in this canton The canton has an area of 44.62 km². In 2011, 288,054 people lived there. ==References== Category:San José Province Category:Cantons of Costa Rica Category:1848 establishments Category:19th-century establishments in Costa Rica Category:1840s establishments in North America
